# Sample requests for agent integration (localhost, adjust APP_PORT if needed)

### Upsert phone model
POST http://localhost:8000/api/agents/devices/models
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Samsung",
  "model_name": "Galaxy S26",
  "variant": "Ultra",
  "announce_date": "2026-02-10",
  "release_date": "2026-03-01",
  "screen": {
    "size_inch": 6.8,
    "technology": "AMOLED",
    "refresh_rate_hz": 120
  }
}

### Generate keywords inside backend (replace ID)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/agents/keywords/generate?phone_model_id=1

### Bulk save ready-made keywords (replace ID)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/agents/keywords/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_model_id": 1,
  "phrases": [
    "дисплей galaxy s26 ultra",
    "экран galaxy s26 ultra купить",
    "замена дисплея galaxy s26 ultra"
  ],
  "language": "ru",
  "category": "display"
}
